{"story":{"group_1":[{"bg":"bg_adv_13041.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story02","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301101,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300801,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameNarration":"御崎 海香","narration":"かずみとカオルを探していた@かこさんと私…","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"その途中で、かこさんの魔法少女仲間の@志伸あきらさんと会うことができた…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300801}],"nameLeft":"夏目 かこ","nameRight":"志伸 あきら","narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"なるほど…@あすなろ市から…！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301101,"motion":400}],"textLeft":"そうなんです…！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300801,"motion":300}],"textRight":"…うーん…でも@あすなろ市の魔法少女か…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300801}],"textRight":"さっきまで店番してたし@自分は会ってないなぁ…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401201,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"御崎 海香","textLeft":"…そうですよね"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300801,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"textRight":"…………"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300801,"motion":100}],"textRight":"だから、ボクも手伝うよ！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":401201,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"[chara:401201:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]え!?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301101,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"夏目 かこ","textLeft":"あきらさん！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300801,"motion":0}],"textRight":"そんな話聞いたら@放っておけないよ"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300801,"motion":200}],"textRight":"それに、人手は多い方が@いいでしょ？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":401201,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"御崎 海香","textLeft":"…ありがとうございます…！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300801,"motion":200}],"textRight":"大丈夫です！@こういうのも性分の内というか…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301101,"motion":400,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"夏目 かこ","textLeft":"『参京院の[textRed:トラブルバスター]』@ですもんね！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300801,"motion":300}],"textRight":"[chara:300801:effect_emotion_sad_0][se:7224_fall_into]…その呼び名は@内心、ちょっと複雑なんだけど…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301101,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"でも、あきらさんがいれば@心強いです！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300801,"motion":0}],"textRight":"…いや…@ボクだけじゃ足りないかな…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401201,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"御崎 海香","textLeft":"足りない…？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300801,"motion":100}],"textRight":"さっきも言った通り@人手は多い方がいいと思うんだ"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300801}],"textRight":"だから、三人よりも@四人、五人と集めれば…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300801,"motion":200}],"textRight":"もっと効率的に@君の友達が探せるはずだよ"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401201,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"それは、確かにそうですが…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300801,"motion":0}],"textRight":"…美雨には連絡した？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_022.exp.json","id":301101,"motion":400,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"夏目 かこ","textLeft":"しました！@[chara:301101:lipSynch_0][wait:0.8][chara:301101:cheek_0][chara:301101:face_mtn_ex_030.exp.json][chara:301101:lipSynch_1]…でも留守電で…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300801,"motion":1}],"textRight":"もう一回電話してみようよ@彼女の力が必要だね…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300801}],"textRight":"彼女と…蒼海幇の…！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301101,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"そ、そうですね！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":401201,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"御崎 海香","textRight":"…そう…かいへい？"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}